data.description: Prime location in the heart of Napoleon! Enjoy all that downtown has to offer including the NORA district, great local business, historic sites & the Maumee River. This charming home has a first floor bedroom and den, main floor bath, 2 generous bedrooms upstairs with a half bath, basement, and ample parking. Eat-in kitchen with plenty of storage + all appliances stay. Relax on the covered patio with fenced backyard & shed big enough for a workshop. Property backs up to St. Augustine so no rear neighbors! High ceilings & desirable floor plan make this home feel even more spacious.
